{"word":"G164 - αἰχμάλωτος - aichmálōtos - aheekh-mal-o-tos' - Captive","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αἰχμάλωτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aichmálōtos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">aheekh-mal-o-tos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Captive</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சிறைப்பட்டவர்கள் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"captive"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From<b>&#x03B1;&#x03B9;&#x0313;&#x03C7;&#x03BC;&#x03B7;&#x0301;</b> <b>aichme&#x0304;</b> (a <i>spear</i>) and a derivative of the same as <a href=\"#/G259 - ἅλωσις - hálōsis - hal'-o-sis/259\">G259</a>; properly a <i>prisoner of war</i>, that is, (generally) a <i>captive:</i> - captive.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G161/161\">G161</a>, <a href=\"#/G162/162\">G162</a>, <a href=\"#/G163/163\">G163</a>, <a href=\"#/G164/164\">G164</a>, <a href=\"#/G4869/4869\">G4869</a>"}]}